            "text": "Week The table shows the frequency of use of Memento as evaluated by log files. The patient ID consists of patient number and group (T for TG) followed by the country code (IT = Italy, AT = Austria, ESP = Spain). Frequency of use is expressed as day of use based on the log file reports. In general, there is a good correspondence between the frequency of use referred by the users in the diary and the log reports. Column \"Implemented in time\": + indicates an increase; -indicates a reduction; = indicates a steady use over time. Other variables potentially related to the frequency are stimulation by the caregiver and general attitude towards technology.",
